<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        .container { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; }
        .header { background-color: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to BlogApp!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name %>,</h2>
            <p>Thanks for joining our community of writers and thinkers! We're excited to see what you'll share with the world.</p>
            <p>Your journey as a blogger starts here. You can now write your first post, follow your favorite authors, and comment on trending topics.</p>
            
            <a href="https://yourblogapp.com/dashboard" class="button">Go to your Dashboard</a>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, just reply to this email. We're happy to help!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 BlogApplication. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>You received this email because you signed up for an account.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>